name: 20 FREE Whoooa! vector and customizable illustrations for your projects
description:
A free version of Whoooa! consists of 20 vectors, handmade and customizable illustrations for your personal projects.


You can change colors at once for all 20 illustrations with just a few clicks in Figma to fit the color palette of your product or brand.


Here's the manual so you can see how easily you can customize it to your own needs https://gregdlubacz.wistia.com/medias/q0e3t1unfr


The entire pack consists of 156 illustrations. You check them out clicking the following link https://www.whoooa.rocks/
